---
title: Ground Pork Carnitas Tacos with Pico de Gallo, Avocadoes and Baby Gems
description: Pork carnitas is a traditional Mexican dish of slow cooked pork shoulder. It's then shredded and pan-fried to give it a crispy texture. We've created a kid-friendly cheat version using ground pork. The secret is cooking the meat until it's very brown!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/ground-pork-carnitas-tacos-493bf6c1.jpg
